metadata.name: Thinking of Home
metadata.description:
digital painting, 2058 x 2936 px  

This is the first piece of my "Backstories" series. 
There's a lot to say about this work, but it doesn't all fit into a description. Also I would like to leave the meaning up to you, before you read about my thoughts on it. 
But if you're interested I invite you to check out my blog post for the whole backstory: 
--> https://peakd.com/hive-158694/@anafae/bunrkllb
